categories: Category:Articles that are known by a nickname

nodes.text: Sneeze was a male. He once went on a mission to the Base Tekar.
Sneeze was a wild eyed man who had unruly, long brown hair. He was always working on the base's speeders. He described himself as a "Soldier and all-round trouble maker".
Sneeze was very loyal to Dineas D' Ink.
